,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":14}],"windowDisplayName":"카논","body":"괜찮을 거 같아!\n감상 한 줄 말고도 간단한 일러스트를 추가하면\n허전하지 않을 거 같아.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":14,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":14,"voiceId":"event91-04-036","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":14}],"windowDisplayName":"카논","body":"이런 느낌으로…… 어떨까?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":14,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":14,"voiceId":"event91-04-037","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":22}],"windowDisplayName":"사요","body":"추워하는…… 해파리 그림 인가요?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":22,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":22,"voiceId":"event91-04-038","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":16}],"windowDisplayName":"아야","body":"굉장해~! 귀엽다!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":16,"motionName":"smile02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":16,"voiceId":"event91-04-039","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":22}],"windowDisplayName":"사요","body":"일러스트를 추가하니 인상이 꽤 변하네요.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":22,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":22,"voiceId":"event91-04-040","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":14}],"windowDisplayName":"카논","body":"에헤헤. 그런가?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":14,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":14,"voiceId":"event91-04-041","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":16}],"windowDisplayName":"아야","body":"고전시의 현대어 번역에 우리다운 예랑 감상.\n거기에 카논 짱의 귀여운 일러스트를 더한\n「백인일수 안내서」!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":16,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":16,"voiceId":"event91-04-042","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":16}],"windowDisplayName":"아야","body":"분명 잘 될 거야! …… 라고는 생각하는데\n어떨까? 사요 짱.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":16,"motionName":"gattsu01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":16,"voiceId":"event91-04-043","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":22}],"windowDisplayName":"사요","body":"그렇군요……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":22,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":22,"voiceId":"event91-04-044","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":22}],"windowDisplayName":"사요","body":"(신경이 쓰이는 점은 「시간」이야.\n이 분량을 대회까지 마무리 할 수 있을지 어떨지.)","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":2,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":22,"motionName":"thinking01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":22,"voiceId":"event91-04-045","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":22}],"windowDisplayName":"사요","body":"(나는 전체적으로 확인해야 하니까 장시간 돕기는 어려워.\n그렇다면 내가 취해야 할 대책은……)","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":2,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[],"voices":[{"characterId":22,"voiceId":"event91-04-046","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":14}],"windowDisplayName":"카논","body":"사요 짱? 저기, 괜찮을까?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":14,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0},{"characterId":16,"motionName":"serious01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":14,"voiceId":"event91-04-047","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":22}],"windowDisplayName":"사요","body":"……네, 물론이에요.\n안내서 제작은 이대로 두 분께 부탁드려도 될까요?","tention":0,"lip